{"title":"活水（外一首）","authors":["陈咏华"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"活水（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈咏华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水，我要为破冰而生的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献出长虹般的赞美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不唱江河新波涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要这样赞美水——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是儿童脸蛋上桃红的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是老人眼角笑出的热泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是幸福的少男少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清澈的眼波闪动的光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是厂矿繁忙车如流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是乡村活跃鱼摇尾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是运动场上波澜起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是哨所军刀夜露坠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是公园鲜花泉边开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是婆娑春柳湖上垂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山中新林云里站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是海里风帆浪中追。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是雪山情深恋草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是井冈意浓想延水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中南海的碧波清且亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清亮在亿万心坎内。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望已经变活力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活力正在血中沸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有源头活水在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间到处都有美！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山斜月更圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水平江倍宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傍山依水新娘船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送行的姐妹围一圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似繁花闹江畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山月浸得江水暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道舟轻嫁妆少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满船载江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾过江先一笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带走江南春一半。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正听得江北歌声传——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南新花昨夜开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江北香风清晨鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔岸春风不会远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿两岸。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}